From: Britt Davis@ENRON on 09/07/2000 10:23 PM
To: Alan Aronowitz/HOU/ECT@ECT, Harry M Collins/HOU/ECT@ECT, Michael A 
Robison/HOU/ECT@ECT, Richard B Sanders/HOU/ECT@ECT, Linda R 
