cargo here, BOTH SENIPAH CONDENSATE CARGOES WERE FOR FGH and

 (c)  whether there were any contamination problems/concerns. NO. NOTE 
HOWEVER THAT "ASHING" METHOD WAS USED BY SGS ON BOTH FEB AND MAY SENIPAH 
CARGOES
 
